I spend my whole day in the cold. This year I’m getting winter ready by using @burtsbeesca lip care products everywhere I go — they are 100% natural origin and provide 4 hours of hydration to repair extremely dry lips (like mine!)

united through everything • looking back on a wonderful GP season
•
📸: @jmfotoz / @isufigureskating
disposables 2022
nyc throwback — why not 🚇

We had the absolute pleasure of having a chat with the incredible Piper Gilles & Paul Poirier the current Grand- Prix Final Champions , and Olympic Icons from Canada. This week we are skating to “Don’t Cry for me Argentina” from
Evita, in which Piper and Paul have their Evita themed free dance this year. We were honored to take some tips and listen to some points of wisdom from the two going into our performance tonight. Thanks Piper and Paul ! 

Thanks to our Cam crew @rikki_lawton
 & @ttomhall #dancingonice
